race.comment: PAT CARD (3) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (21.88) at Cannington in a Grade 5 over 381m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can continue the winning form. INCREDIBLE HEART (1) ran good time (29.67) winning a Grade 5/6 at Northam when jumping from this same box. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. GOUDA MONELLI (8) finished in the minors last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 488m at this track, taking a Grade 5/6 in a speedy 27.28. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. TIC TAC MONELLI (7) must be respected at her pet distance.
